comments: Holiday (DAL) is absorbing the initial contact that occurs with Vanderbilt (LAL) and incidental contact occurs as Vanderbilt moves under the pick.
Davis (LAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds without actively guarding Powell (DAL) when the shot is attempted.
Irving (DAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard Schroder (LAL).
Bullock (DAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Holiday (DAL) legally defends James' (LAL) driving shot attempt.
Schroder (LAL) momentarily brings his arm toward Doncic's (DAL) path as they engage in the post, and marginal contact occurs as Doncic moves it away.
James (LAL) legally contests Bullock's (DAL) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Irving (DAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Wood (DAL) and Davis (LAL) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Doncic (DAL) makes contact with the ball prior to the ensuing arm contact with Davis (LAL), which is marginal.
Irving (DAL) momentarily grasps Schroder's (LAL) right arm before quickly releasing and marginal contact occurs as he secures the rebound.
Wood (DAL) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Doncic (DAL) rests a slight hand on Davis' (LAL) side and marginal contact occurs as he contests the jump shot attempt.
Vanderbilt (LAL) legally defends Doncic (DAL) during the in-bounds pass.
Doncic (DAL) taps the ball back into the frontcourt prior to landing in the backcourt.
Wood (DAL) commits a take foul on Schroder (LAL).
Bullock (DAL) grabs and holds Davis (LAL), affecting his FOM as he reaches for the ball. The illegal contact occurs after the release of James' (LAL) in-bounds pass.
Irving (DAL) goes to, not through, Schroder's (LAL) space and marginal contact occurs as Irving releases away on the perimeter.
Following the made basket, Doncic (DAL) makes contact with the ball as the timeout is being called.
Holiday (DAL) lightly brushes Schroder's (LAL) backside as he attempts to commit a take foul.
Irving (DAL) commits a take foul on Schroder (LAL).
